parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Timing Chain Failure and Related Engine Damage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause engine damage, leading to costly repairs, and potentially leaving the driver stranded or causing accidents.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine performance issues can cause poor acceleration, stalling, and misfires, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle has no power when driving
rotten egg/sulfur smell emitted from exhaust
and engine skips with strong jerking when moderately accelerating.
